# Copy to `.dev.vars` and fill in. Same KEY=VALUE format wrangler uses.
# Used by both `wrangler dev` and the local backup runner (src/local.ts).
# `.dev.vars` is gitignored — never commit real secrets.

# Account mnemonic for signing registration transactions (required to register).
MNEMONIC="word1 word2 word3 ... word25"

# Optional sender address override, for rekeyed accounts. Leave unset otherwise.
# SENDER=REGISTRY2UJANM5G2G45MZD4DKPH7RPBDJRJ3HSFDPO4IY7HKU5ZY4MLV4

# --- Local backup runner only (ignored by wrangler) ---

# Cursor file path. Default: ./.local-state/cursors.json
# STATE_FILE=/var/lib/escreg/cursors.json

# Poll interval in ms for `npm run local`. Default: 60000
# INTERVAL_MS=60000
